      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "このままだと今夜の夕飯は食べるものがないよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.2666660309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さ～く～ら～？　魚を買うお金を全部『魚魚っとさん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.63333203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "ガチャガチャ』につぎ込んだのは誰だったかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.7999987285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だ、だって……どうしても『黄金爆レア魚魚っとさん』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.0333322842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
